{"tid":2027284,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「一生毒奶計劃」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:49:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fc2c6c4be36824dca8144a93136f47243920f59f","tid":2027284,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:49:06.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200521/20921482/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200521%2F20921482%2F&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoV1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=056be73d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200521%2F20921482%2F&h=07a3ef97\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200521/20921482/</a><br />\n<br />\n「一生毒奶計劃」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200521/large/1589960933_3f52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200521%2Flarge%2F1589960933_3f52.jpg&h=b6ec4b57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原定每年3月初召開的全國「人大」及「政協」兩會，今年受武漢肺炎疫情影響，分別推遲至5月21及22日召開。<br />\n<br />\n即使推遲，但年年都出現有趣現象，不少政客為了吸睛，製造話題，媚主表忠，刷存在感，紛紛提出奇特建議。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大代表，內蒙古某奶製品集團的品質檢測控制中心主任李翠枝，建議「中國人一生飲奶計劃」，希望透過飲奶來改善中國人體質，「為全民健康保駕護航」云云。<br />\n<br />\n先不說<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n祭品&hellip;&hellip;都由中國大陸惡名昭彰的毒奶相伴，這一輩子多慘痛！<br />\n<br />\n回想2008年大陸三聚氰胺毒奶粉事件，令多少嬰兒成了腎結石大頭娃娃，<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n也許他們認為不以尋釁滋事罪把父母抓捕坐牢就很對得起了。<br />\n<br />\n在充斥假、劣、毒奶製品卻無法無天的國家，又哄又騙又迫人民一生飲國產奶？是什麼變態心理？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}